'''Quints''' were tall, furred [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] species hailing from the planet [[Quint (planet)|Quint]] in the [[Quint system/Legends|Quint system]] located in the [[Inner Rim/Legends|Inner Rim]]. They were best known for their speed and agility. Quints were covered in delicate [[Hair/Legends|fur]], and had small heads with triangular [[Eye/Legends|eyes]].

